{"tid":1213213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你仲諗緊去塞地鐵定立法會,不如你入嚟睇下","createTime":"2019-06-13T00:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T01:51:51.000Z","uid":169479,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2e6501e8d9080b1794fafa825ed1bb107eddf975","tid":1213213,"uid":169479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:57:30.000Z","msg":"先不論有沒鬼，當呢到所有人都係義士先<br />\n我地目標係阻止逃犯條例 ！<br />\n最快嘅方法一定係阻止開會<br />\n我明一定有人驚係流料，白白去咗立法會個邊 <br />\n但如果係真，你就會係調景嶺個頭望住個會開咗<br />\n不合作運動係好<br />\n但林鄭都唔驚103萬人，更何況條例一過，你仲會唔會做不合作運動？定你相信佢會撤回？<br />\n當然呢啲係我主觀諗法，唔一定全面客觀，會有人唔服，要去塞地鐵，都會有人話驚要休息唔出。<br />\n我明。<br />\n但其他唔怕嘅、仲可以捱嘅，請你諗下今日要做咩。<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36fe2674b773aa5e6d785fc4845ed5e475b9817","tid":1213213,"uid":236140,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:58:20.000Z","msg":"梁美芬已經成功入咗立法會"},{"pid":"376ec515d30abfac963c50f0b27d3473376fc5c8","tid":1213213,"uid":223374,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:58:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10ef33eec74d7af944d53b16142d9049aac7e01e","tid":1213213,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:59:15.000Z","msg":"全香港得地鐵一種交通工具？<br />\n<br />\n弱智"},{"pid":"6e2877ab51e9db5796216f3cb5d32d1f73ec0a6a","tid":1213213,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:59:42.000Z","msg":"立會嚴重唔夠人 唔建議去"},{"pid":"99e1891ab9fbc7a3edb73a3a8dc3f6e9ac04aef9","tid":1213213,"uid":87985,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:00:04.000Z","msg":"阻止二讀最重要!"},{"pid":"486edb1e61ea0813f30bb1a2caef33607a7ba4a0","tid":1213213,"uid":149026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:00:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e4c339693a76e0eb612169de8a124896cad36d5","tid":1213213,"uid":200322,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:00:47.000Z","msg":"<i